QuestData.Title: History Heist
QuestData.Description:
When the Primalists raided our village, they took more than our lives; they stole the heart |L303-of our community|l--our priceless historical documents!
I will not stand for records of our traditions, |L303-rituals, and rich history taken from us! We still have lessons to learn from them.|l
Please, recover them from those looting Primalist scouts |L303-so they can be preserved!|l
